title: Coverking Custom Fit Dashboard Cover for Select Chevrolet S10 Models - Velour (Break-Up)
features: Made from a premium polyester material with a smooth Velour finish for softness and durability
The three layers of polyester fabric is fade-resistant and creates a more durable cover for protecting your dash from cracks, spills, stains, or other damage
Custom tailored to your specific make, model, year, and configuration and constructed using a zig-zag stitch, which allows the cover to hug the contours of the dashboard surface
Cover protects against extreme heat from the sun and damaging UV rays as well as reduces dangerous glare while driving

description: Velour Custom Dash Covers now comes with three unique designs from one of the most trusted name in camouflage. Coverking's top of the line velour is custom manufactured using unique zigzag stitching allowing the best fit for your vehicle. Coverking's covers come standard with all cutouts for airbags, sensors or other accessories on your car.
